<div class="wrapper wrapper_padding clearfix">
  <div class="col-1 about homepage_content">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <hr>

    <p id="textwrap"> I have always loved to solve problems. Being adept at math and science,
      I graduated and worked as an industrial engineer before becoming a full
      stack web developer. I enjoy 3D printing, traveling, and hobby
      electronics. My varied experiences allow me to provide a novel perspective
      through my problem solving and leadership skills developed as an engineer.
      Most importantly, I love the challenge of coding and continual learning.
    </p>

    <!-- <img src="images/MatthewRoche.jpg" alt="Matthew Roche"> -->
  </div>

  <div class="col-2 homepage_content">
    <h2> Articles </h2>
    <hr>
    <% @posts.each do |post| %>
      <h3><a href="#"> <%= link_to post.title, post %> </a></h3>
      <p class ="date"> <%= post.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d") %> </p>
    <% end %>

  </div>

  <div class="col-3 homepage_content">
    <h2> Latest Builds </h2>
    <hr>
    <% @projects.each do |project| %>
      <h3><a href="#"> <%= link_to project.title, project %> </a></h3>
      <p class ="date"> <%= project.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d") %> </p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
